Package: apt-health
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Aman <aman@example.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/aman-ali07/apt-health
Depends: bash (>= 4.0), apt (>= 1.0), dpkg (>= 1.15)
Description: Safe APT/DPKG diagnostics and fixes
 A production-ready CLI tool to detect common APT/DPKG issues,
 safely apply fixes, and provide clear system status information.
 The tool checks for interrupted operations, broken dependencies,
 locked APT processes, corrupted caches, and held packages, then
 applies safe fixes in the correct order.
